column5: Come and enjoy this beautiful Lakefront Texas size home of nearly 6,000 square feet (600 square meters) with 5 bedrooms - only 15 minutes drive from NASA; 10 mins. from the Kemah boardwalk, 25 mins. from Galveston Island and Hobby airport; 35 mins to the world-famous Texas Medical Center.
column8: CASA GRANDE - NEAR HOUSTON AND NASA
